Description:
Annotation on the envelope: "Rubens Neues Testament Passion" addressed (inside) to "Herrn Professor Dr. H. G. Evers Technische Hochschule Lehrschül für Kunstgeschichte 61 - Darmstadt Germany"

- Envelope addressed to "Herrn Professor Hans Gerhard Evers Technische Hochschüle Darmstadt" dated 14.01.1959, with correspondence with Anny Ettle and the photocopy of a reproduction of 'The Crowning with Thorns'
- Bibliographic references
